dct_description_sm: United States. Army Map Service. Alternate title: Safi. In upper left margin: Morocco 1:10,000. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. N.W. Africa zone grid. "Advance ed." 1942, by Corps of Engineers, was indexed as part of series G. S. G. S. 4241. Compiled from French H.O. chart 5465, 1913, 1936. Revision, R.A.F. aerial photographs and Michelin Tourist Guide, 1939.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
